nodes.text: The Clone Wars: Opress Unleashed is an issue of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars comic series. It is a free issue available as part of Free Comic Book Day on May 7, 2011, and was bundled as a flip cover with Avatar: The Last Airbender on the opposite side. It was an excerpt from the upcoming standalone comic The Clone Wars: Strange Allies.
